                                                               java.lang.Integer projectId,

        Find the top entities of a type which has highest rating.
        Parameters:
        descriptor - The descriptor about the InterwikiReference, contains entity-type and artifact-type as filter.
        projectId - Optional project-id filter, only those entities, which belong to this project.
        numEntities - The number of entities to list
        Returns:
        List of ObjectRatingStatsDto of that type.

      • findMostHighlyRatedTrackerItems

                                                                   java.lang.String[] allowedStatusNames,
                                                                   java.lang.String[] deniedStatusNames)
        Find the highest rated TrackerItemDtos.
        Parameters:
        projectId - Optional project-id filter, only issues from this project are listed.
        trackerId - Optional tracker-id filter, only issues from this tracker are listed.
        numEntities -
        allowedStatusNames - The name strings for the statuses allowed only. If null/empty then all is allowed
        deniedStatusNames - The name strings for the denied statuses. If null/empty then nothing is denied
        Returns:
        List of ObjectRatingStatsDto of that type.
